{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-21-amicable-numbers","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 21: Brojevi za prijatelje","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Neka je d(<code>n</code>) definisano kao zbir stvarnih delilaca od <code>n</code> (brojevi manji od <code>n</code> koji dele <code>n</code> bez ostatka).</p>\n<p>Ako je d(<code>a</code>) = <code>b</code> i d(<code>b</code>) = <code>a</code>, pri čemu je <code>a</code> ≠ <code>b</code>, tada su <code>a</code> i <code>b</code> prijateljski par, a svaki od njih naziva se prijateljski broj.</p>\n<p>Na primer, delitelji 220 su 1, 2, 4, 5, 10, 11, 20, 22, 44, 55 i 110; stoga d(220) = 284. Delitelji 284 su 1, 2, 4, 71 i 142; pa d(284) = 220.</p>\n<p>Izračunajte ukupnu sumu svih brojeva za kompatibilnost ispod <code>n</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3811000cf542c50fe94","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301851,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-21-amicable-numbers"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function sumAmicableNum(n) {\n\n  return n;\n}\n\nsumAmicableNum(10000);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>sumAmicableNum(1000)</code> treba da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert.isNumber(sumAmicableNum(1000));"},{"text":"<p><code>sumAmicableNum(1000)</code> trebalo bi da vrati 504.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(sumAmicableNum(1000), 504);"},{"text":"<p><code>sumAmicableNum(2000)</code> trebalo bi da vrati 2898.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(sumAmicableNum(2000), 2898);"},{"text":"<p><code>sumAmicableNum(5000)</code> treba da vrati 8442.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(sumAmicableNum(5000), 8442);"},{"text":"<p><code>sumAmicableNum(10000)</code> inapaswa kurudisha 31626.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(sumAmicableNum(10000), 31626);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-1-to-100","dashedName":"problem-21-amicable-numbers","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-22-names-scores","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-20-factorial-digit-sum","id":"5900f3811000cf542c50fe94","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function arrangedProbability(limit) {\n  // Based on https://www.mathblog.dk/project-euler-100-blue-discs-two-blue/\n  let blue = 15;\n  let discs = 21;\n\n  while (discs < limit) {\n    const nextBlue = 3 * blue + 2 * discs - 2;\n    const nextDiscs = 4 * blue + 3 * discs - 3;\n\n    blue = nextBlue;\n    discs = nextDiscs;\n  }\n  return blue;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-21-amicable-numbers"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}